divs: Sighting DetailsI have a game cam that I put out at night to see the local wildlife. My game cam picks up heat and is set to record for 15 second. After many taping, I have not ever seen anything like this.The game cam was looking over a golf coarse and the houses in the back ground are about 200 yrds. away.
Summary: 2 sets of lights in a line
